=Description=


"BitVault is a P2P based content-addressable retention platform for large volume of reference data that needs to be retained for a long period. BitVault uses P2P technologies for its self-managing and self-healing capabilities and uses massively parallel repair to reduce vulnerability window of data loss. The simplicity of the architecture relies on an eventually reliable membership service provided by a perfect one-hop [[Distributed Hash Table]]."
(http://thothzone.blogspot.com/2006/07/p2p-buzz-to-biz.html)


